Title: HYBRID / BATTERY CONTROL: FRAME WIRE: INSTALLATION; 2019 - 2022 MY Prius [12/2018 -        ]

INSTALLATION

PROCEDURE

1. INSTALL HV BATTERY PACK WIRE (for NICKEL METAL HYDRIDE BATTERY)

CAUTION:

Wear insulated gloves.

(a) Engage the 7 clamps to install the HV battery pack wire.

2. INSTALL HV FLOOR UNDER WIRE (for NICKEL METAL HYDRIDE BATTERY)

CAUTION:

Wear insulated gloves.

(a) Engage the clamp (B).

(b) Install a new clamp (A).

(c) Insert the HV floor under wire into the floor panel hole and engage the grommet.

(d) Install 3 new clamps in the order shown in the illustration.

(e) Install the HV floor under wire with the 2 nuts.

Torque:

8.5 N·m {87 kgf·cm, 75 in·lbf}

(f) Engage the clamp.

(g) Engage the 5 clamps.

(h) Engage the 2 clamps.

3. INSTALL HV FLOOR UNDER WIRE (for LITHIUM-ION BATTERY)

CAUTION:

Wear insulated gloves.

(a) Engage the clamp (B).

(b) Install a new clamp (A).

(c) Insert the HV floor under wire into the floor panel hole and engage the grommet.

(d) Install 3 new clamps in the order shown in the illustration.

(e) Install the HV floor under wire with the 2 nuts.

Torque:

8.5 N·m {87 kgf·cm, 75 in·lbf}

4. CONNECT NO. 2 PARKING BRAKE CABLE ASSEMBLY

(a) Connect the No. 2 parking brake cable assembly with the 2 bolts.

Torque:

6.0 N·m {61 kgf·cm, 53 in·lbf}

HINT:

Click here

10. CONNECT HV FLOOR UNDER WIRE (for NICKEL METAL HYDRIDE BATTERY)

Click here

11. INSTALL INVERTER TERMINAL COVER (for NICKEL METAL HYDRIDE BATTERY)

Click here

12. CONNECT WIRE HARNESS

CAUTION:

Wear insulated gloves.

(a) Connect the shield ground to the HV battery.

(b) Connect the 2 HV battery junction block assembly connectors.

NOTICE:

Make sure that the connectors are connected securely.

31. CONNECT HV FLOOR UNDER WIRE

32. CONNECT ENGINE WIRE

CAUTION:

Wear insulated gloves.

NOTICE:

Do not allow any foreign matter or water to enter the inverter with converter assembly.

(a) Engage the 2 clamps and connect the engine wire.

(b) Install the bolt.

Torque:

8.0 N·m {82 kgf·cm, 71 in·lbf}

(c) Connect the 2 inverter with converter assembly connectors and move each lock lever as shown in the illustration.

NOTICE:

  • To prevent damage due to static electricity, do not touch the terminals of the disconnected connectors.
  • Do not damage the terminals, connector housing or inverter with converter assembly when connecting the connectors.
  • Do not touch the waterproof seal or terminals of the connector.
